data.description: NEW ROOF!  Discover your Dream Home in the sought after Brittany Ridge Estates subdivision with this spacious 4 bed, 3.5 bath GEM! Step into luxury as your greeted with natural light and vaulted ceilings on the main level that has an office (Perfect for those who work from HOME), great room, half bath and large eat in kitchen. Some features of the kitchen include custom cabinets, bamboo flooring and pantry.  The second level offers a large master suite with stunning see-through fireplace that adds a touch of elegance and looks through to the master bath that includes huge soaking tub, shower and very spacious walk in closet.  New carpet throughout.  Enjoy the Serenity of your own Private Deck, perfect for Hosting Gatherings and Outdoor Entertainment..  While the basement is currently unfinished, it is set up with a workout room and it presents an opportunity to create a space that perfectly suits your vision.  Located in a Cul-de-sac, don't miss out on making this exceptional property your Own.
